@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_itugae(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.83) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.56)) / v1)
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = v1
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin(v2)
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.07 + v1 + 0.24) - (v1 + 0.48 - tmp + 0.47)) * ((tmp + 0.23 + tmp + 0.36) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.19)))
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
